HEADWORD: peace-loving
<hw>peace-loving</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Inclined or disposed to
peace; <as>as, <ex>peace-loving</ex> citizens</as>. Opposed to
<ant>warlike</ant> or <ant>belligerent</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> peaceable, dovish, pacific.</syn>⟦br⟧
